{"tid":1096781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《唐人街》:撼贏陳展鵬！唐詩詠竟然係全劇最好打","createTime":"2019-04-08T02:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T14:27:10.000Z","uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6a43d6092e7fe4141aa9bbf34901ae09ce282587","tid":1096781,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"食錯乜，個樣變咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n==================<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1RU1kv2DkgPgkroyfPJVQ0viHIZbKSMff\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1RU1kv2DkgPgkroyfPJVQ0viHIZbKSMff&h=ee3836e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1cgD9RZAh1GRpC9tvamlygy8-haY3_yly\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1cgD9RZAh1GRpC9tvamlygy8-haY3_yly&h=784367a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1hE7_vukzvIVq6K7n_iHm7DeQLPQu_7IZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1hE7_vukzvIVq6K7n_iHm7DeQLPQu_7IZ&h=69e0e47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1QbiSp0sUnOa_GYR8OynkBwjAkjpWwu56\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1QbiSp0sUnOa_GYR8OynkBwjAkjpWwu56&h=339dbf18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1Bj6gR8yQCl-yvICbWT1Qj2rQbsRpfvdN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1Bj6gR8yQCl-yvICbWT1Qj2rQbsRpfvdN&h=f115deda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=12I-V7ZP4KYl7YLXAPQBWoRSYLkFKkR2F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D12I-V7ZP4KYl7YLXAPQBWoRSYLkFKkR2F&h=94eb7214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1oBPNrVZYthj9woA5XOmzuNZqxSfwRjPX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1oBPNrVZYthj9woA5XOmzuNZqxSfwRjPX&h=e926f7a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1eUmOUBizoHdUYnBY_kKz5ldpd9YjZCCP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1eUmOUBizoHdUYnBY_kKz5ldpd9YjZCCP&h=78f67ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1PN3sI8H__rzLLrrVXWlOhFMUqCBjlEaW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1PN3sI8H__rzLLrrVXWlOhFMUqCBjlEaW&h=4039f50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1m-XKwZGX8T3pmy6fkE3JJimVFmRQMq2h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1m-XKwZGX8T3pmy6fkE3JJimVFmRQMq2h&h=c696d0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唐詩詠今次做打女，令人耳目一新！<br />\n<br />\n藝人唐詩詠與陳展鵬、陳山聰、伍允龍、王君馨和姚子羚等日前齊集將軍澳電視城，為劇集《唐人街》開工。令人意想不到的是，詩詠是今次劇中最好打角色，她笑言記招式比背對白更難：「從來冇人會覺得我係打得，今次做到，辛苦得嚟好開心。（點說服觀眾？）交畀監製同武術指導，我盡量配合，大家都好幫我練習，我只係打咗一場，最辛苦嘅仲未拍，記招式好難，一錯就好易有人受傷。我最怕整到人，我自己好彩暫時都只係瘀傷，未有大傷，希望大家繼續冇事。」<br />\n<br />\n講到其緋聞男友「教育界王力宏」Samuel被影到接載其他女士，因而被指花弗，詩詠無奈直言：「我哋係朋友，咁其實我都會車男仔放工，冇乜嘢，我都驚影響到人嘅生活，幫佢嘅就係講少啲。（撐佢唔花弗？）唔好講到咁嚴重，我都成日車人收工」<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n東網巨星開咗ig喇，大家快啲follow<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JjSVcr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JjSVcr&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=4f3d08a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JjSVcr</a><br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=c762c66c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc</a><br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++"},{"pid":"9258c4d8b7edc2e287e19fae5ab1036715295ee5","tid":1096781,"uid":48905,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DLZB1B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DLZB1B.png&h=80a83519&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f4f47d7030413d02c15eb7fad35e7ae96284cf","tid":1096781,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:57:30.000Z","msg":"套野叫城寨英雄?"},{"pid":"ac1392ecdfb0d0142949bbd38ba639e870b84360","tid":1096781,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天生唐高貴艷麗到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf565c6ea47477afe85f32710ab3841118a8f56","tid":1096781,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"又有王君馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3882668d3f41812c8d5946dd9752225d57aaee19","tid":1096781,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"扮胡定欣？"},{"pid":"391e05a02da76ea4ffa85105ca5b8b9f634c39ad","tid":1096781,"uid":3369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係教育界王力宏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963fe611a8cb66c762bb3c9f59d6bfee63e20564","tid":1096781,"uid":152